'''纖恙蟎'''（學名：{{lang|la|''Leptotrombidium deliense''}}），又名'''地里恙蟎'''<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cdc.gov.tw/uploads/files/201205/e7a08362-939e-4306-b5b4-68f7ec8c90ad.pdf |title=恙蟲病病媒之種類與生態 |publisher=衛生署疾病管制局研究檢驗中心 |author=王錫杰 |date=2012-05-22 |access-date=2021-09-27 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2021-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210927171934/https://www.cdc.gov.tw/uploads/files/201205/e7a08362-939e-4306-b5b4-68f7ec8c90ad.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，俗稱'''沙蚤'''，是一種[[恙蟎科|恙蟎科]]的蟎，屬於[[寄蟎總目|寄蟎總目]]的[[恙蟎目|恙蟎目]][[恙蟎科|恙蟎科]][[鉤恙蟎屬|鉤恙蟎屬]]。牠們主要在濃密的[[灌木|灌木]]叢植被生活。纖恙蟎是[[恙蟲病|恙蟲病]]的載體<ref name="AchaSzyfres2003">{{cite book|author1=Pedro N. Acha|author2=Boris Szyfres|title=Zoonoses and Communicable Diseases Common to Man and Animals: Chlamydioses, rickettsioses, and viroses|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=SKd2hN1hb64C&pg=PA40|accessdate=2010-04-13|year=2003|publisher=Pan American Health Org|isbn=9789275119921|pages=40–}}</ref>，其唾液帶有[[恙蟲東方體|恙蟲東方體]]（{{lang|la|''Orientia tsutsugamushi''}}）<ref name="pmid18281226">{{cite journal |author=Tseng BY, Yang HH, Liou JH, Chen LK, Hsu YH |title=Immunohistochemical study of scrub typhus: a report of two cases |journal=Kaohsiung J. Med. Sci. |volume=24 |issue=2 |pages=92–8 |date=2008-02 |pmid=18281226 |doi=10.1016/S1607-551X(08)70103-7 |url=http://ajws.elsevier.com/ajws_pubmed/pubmed_switch.asp?journal_issn=1607-551X&art_pub_year=2008&%20art_pub_month=02&art_pub_vol=24&art_sp=92 |access-date=2010-09-19 |archive-date=2012-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120215233219/http://ajws.elsevier.com/ajws_pubmed/pubmed_switch.asp?journal_issn=1607-551X&art_pub_year=2008&%20art_pub_month=02&art_pub_vol=24&art_sp=92 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，並透過咬野生的[[囓齒類|囓齒類]]動物或人類來傳播疾病<ref name="AchaSzyfres2003" />。

